00080 // ----- radix_tree_add ---------------------------------------------
00084 int radix_tree_add(SRadixTree * pTree, uint32_t uKey,
00085                    uint8_t uKeyLen, void * pItem)
00086 {
00087   SRadixTreeItem ** ppTreeItem= &pTree->pRoot;
00088   uint8_t uLen= uKeyLen;
00089 
00090   // Go to given 'key/len' position. Create path along the way if
00091   // required...
00092   // Warning: '*ppTreeItem' is used to add new nodes while
00093   // 'ppTreeItem' is used to keep track of the current node !!
00094   while (uLen > 0) {
00095     if (*ppTreeItem == NULL)
00096       *ppTreeItem= radix_tree_item_create(NULL);
00097     if (uKey & (1 << (pTree->uKeyLen-(uKeyLen+1-uLen))))
00098       ppTreeItem= &(*ppTreeItem)->pRight;
00099     else
00100       ppTreeItem= &(*ppTreeItem)->pLeft;
00101     uLen--;
00102   }
00103 
00104   if (*ppTreeItem == NULL) {
00105     *ppTreeItem= radix_tree_item_create(pItem);
00106   } else {
00107     // If a previous value exists, replace it
00108     if ((*ppTreeItem)->pItem != NULL) {
00109       if (pTree->fDestroy != NULL)
00110         pTree->fDestroy(&(*ppTreeItem)->pItem);
00111     }
00112     // Set new value
00113     (*ppTreeItem)->pItem= pItem;
00114   }
00115 
00116   return 0;
00117 }

00119 // ----- radix_tree_remove ------------------------------------------
00124 int radix_tree_remove(SRadixTree * pTree, uint32_t uKey,
00125                       uint8_t uKeyLen)
00126 {
00127   SStack * pStack= stack_create(pTree->uKeyLen);
00128   uint8_t uLen= uKeyLen;
00129   SRadixTreeItem ** ppTreeItem= &pTree->pRoot;
00130   
00131   while (uLen > 0) {
00132     if (*ppTreeItem == NULL)
00133       return -1;
00134     if (uKey & (1 << (pTree->uKeyLen-(uKeyLen+1-uLen)))) {
00135       if ((*ppTreeItem)->pRight != NULL) {
00136         stack_push(pStack, ppTreeItem);
00137         ppTreeItem= &(*ppTreeItem)->pRight;
00138       } else
00139         return -1;
00140     } else {
00141       if ((*ppTreeItem)->pLeft != NULL) {
00142         stack_push(pStack, ppTreeItem);
00143         ppTreeItem= &(*ppTreeItem)->pLeft;
00144       } else
00145         return -1;
00146     }
00147     uLen--;
00148   }
00149   if ((*ppTreeItem == NULL) || ((*ppTreeItem)->pItem == NULL))
00150     return -1;
00151   radix_tree_item_destroy(ppTreeItem, pTree->fDestroy);
00152   while (stack_depth(pStack) > 0) {
00153     ppTreeItem= (SRadixTreeItem **) stack_pop(pStack);
00154     if (((*ppTreeItem)->pLeft == NULL) &&
00155         ((*ppTreeItem)->pRight == NULL) &&
00156         ((*ppTreeItem)->pItem == NULL)) {
00157       radix_tree_item_destroy(ppTreeItem, pTree->fDestroy);
00158     } else
00159       break;
00160   }
00161   stack_destroy(&pStack);
00162   return 0;
00163 }

00197 // ----- radix_tree_get_best ----------------------------------------
00201 void * radix_tree_get_best(SRadixTree * pTree,
00202                            uint32_t uKey,
00203                            uint8_t uKeyLen)
00204 {
00205   uint8_t uLen= uKeyLen;
00206   SRadixTreeItem * pTreeItem= pTree->pRoot;
00207   void * pResult= NULL;
00208 
00209   if (pTreeItem == NULL)
00210     return NULL;
00211   if (pTreeItem->pItem != NULL)
00212     pResult= pTreeItem->pItem;
00213   while (uLen > 0) {
00214     if ((pTreeItem != NULL) && (pTreeItem->pItem != NULL))
00215       pResult= pTreeItem->pItem;
00216     if (uKey & (1 << (pTree->uKeyLen-(uKeyLen+1-uLen)))) {
00217       if (pTreeItem->pRight != NULL)
00218         pTreeItem= pTreeItem->pRight;
00219     } else {
00220       if (pTreeItem->pLeft != NULL)
00221         pTreeItem= pTreeItem->pLeft;
00222     }
00223     uLen--;
00224     if ((pTreeItem != NULL) && (pTreeItem->pItem != NULL))
00225       pResult= pTreeItem->pItem;
00226   }
00227   
00228   return pResult;
00229 }

00237 // ----- radix_tree_for_each ----------------------------------------
00241 int radix_tree_for_each(SRadixTree * pTree,
00242                         FRadixTreeForEach fForEach,
00243                         void * pContext)
00244 {
00245   SStack * pStack= stack_create(pTree->uKeyLen);
00246   SRadixTreeItem * pTreeItem;
00247   SRadixTreeForEachContext * pStackContext;
00248   int iResult= 0;
00249   uint32_t uKey;
00250   uint8_t uKeyLen;
00251 
00252   pTreeItem= pTree->pRoot;
00253   uKey= 0;
00254   uKeyLen= 0;
00255   // Depth first search
00256   while (pTreeItem != NULL) {
00257     if (pTreeItem->pItem != NULL) {
00258       iResult= fForEach(uKey, uKeyLen, pTreeItem->pItem, pContext);
00259       if (iResult != 0)
00260         return iResult;
00261     }
00262     if (pTreeItem->pLeft != NULL) {
00263       if (pTreeItem->pRight != NULL) {
00264         pStackContext= (SRadixTreeForEachContext *)
00265           MALLOC(sizeof(SRadixTreeForEachContext));
00266         pStackContext->pTreeItem= pTreeItem->pRight;
00267         pStackContext->uKeyLen= uKeyLen+1;
00268         pStackContext->uKey= uKey+(1 << (pTree->uKeyLen-uKeyLen-1));
00269         stack_push(pStack, pStackContext);
00270       }
00271       pTreeItem= pTreeItem->pLeft;
00272       uKeyLen++;
00273     } else if (pTreeItem->pRight != NULL) {
00274       pTreeItem= pTreeItem->pRight;
00275       uKey= uKey+(1 << (pTree->uKeyLen-uKeyLen-1));
00276       uKeyLen++;
00277     } else {
00278       if (stack_depth(pStack) > 0) {
00279         pStackContext= (SRadixTreeForEachContext *) stack_pop(pStack);
00280         pTreeItem= pStackContext->pTreeItem;
00281         uKey= pStackContext->uKey;
00282         uKeyLen= pStackContext->uKeyLen;
00283         FREE(pStackContext);
00284       } else
00285         break;
00286     }
00287   }
00288   stack_destroy(&pStack);
00289   return 0;
00290 }
